    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Term used to describe pigments or dyes that fade or change color due to the action of light. It does not refer to color changes caused by chemical reactions with the atmosphere or surrounding materials.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
